<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=yes">

	
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="" href="~/css/Index.css" />
	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.12.9/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<title>Novel Nest</title>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="carousel-container">
		<h1 class="card-subtitle">Welcome to the Novel Nest</h1>

		<div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h-100">

			<div id="carouselAboutNovelNest" class="carousel-slide" data-ride="carousel">
				<ol class="carousel-indicators">
					<li data-target="#carouselAboutNovelNest" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
					<li data-target="#carouselAboutNovelNest" data-slide-to="1"></li>
					<li data-target="#carouselAboutNovelNest" data-slide-to="2"></li>
				</ol>
				<div class="carousel-inner">
					<div class="carousel-item active">
						<img class="img-carousel" src="/images/Index/girl-reading.jpg" alt="First slide">
						<p>Add all your books to your online library and order them with your own style!</p>
					</div>
					<div class="carousel-item">
						<img class="img-carousel" src="/images/Index/girl-reading-in-grass.jpg" alt="Second slide">
						<p>Give the books you have read reviews, or make a bookshelf of the books you still want or have to read!</p>
					</div>
					<div class="carousel-item">
						<img class="img-carousel" src="/images/Index/books-index.jpg" alt="Third slide">
						<p>Add the books you are currently reading to your nightstand. Keep track of your reading time and add notes!</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p>A new way to keep track of your readings. Make new friends and connect! Click <a href="@Url.Action("LoginPage", "Home")">here</a> to make a new account.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>